Posts.Content: Dimel wrote: I am a 54 year old female. Had mammogram last September. Recalled for second look. They found a lump and said it was a cyst and not to worry. Have recently felt a lump higher up on my left breast almost at my armpit that I have not felt before.. Should I be concerned about this and see a doctor? By the way mother had breast cancer twice in her lifetime. Log in to post a reply
